quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  23,28,"Sε wo ne wͻn a wͻka wo ho no tena nsuom hyεn no mu a, ka sε: “Aseda wͻ Nyankopͻn a Wagye yεn afri nnipa bͻnefoͻ no nsam."
  23,29,"Na ka sε: “Me Wura Nyankopͻn, fa me kɔduru dwoodwoo na Wona Wode (onipa) kɔduru dwoodwoo."
  23,30,"Nokorε sε nsεnkyerεnee wͻ woi mu. Nokorε nso sε Yεn na Yεsͻ (onipa) hwε."
  23,31,"Afei Yεbͻͻ awoͻ ntoatoasoͻ foforͻ wͻ wͻn akyi."
  23,32,"Enti Yεsomaa ͻsomafoͻ fri wͻn mu sε, (ͻnka nkyerε wͻn sε): “Monsom Nyankopͻn, na monni awurade biara ka ne ho, enti monsuro {Nyame} anaa?”"
  23,33,"Ne nkorͻfoͻ no mu ahemfo no a wͻnnye nnie, na wͻbu Daakye nhyiamu no atorͻsεm, na Y’adom wͻn wiase asetena mu ahonyadeε no kaa sε: “Woi yε onipa tesε mo ara; deε modie no mu bi ara na odie, εna deε monom no mu bi ara nso na ͻnom"
  23,34,"Sε modi onipa tesε mo ara akyi a, εneε nokorε sε na moaberε agu paa."
  23,35,"Ɔrehyε mo bͻ sε nokorε, εberε a moawu na moayε mfuturo ne nnompe no, yεbεma mo asan aba (nkwa mu bio)?"
  23,36,"Deε yεrehyε mo ho bͻ no (ne nokorε) ntεm kwan ware, εkwan ware paa."
  23,37,"Ɛno ara ne yεn wiase asetena yi. Yerewu na Yεte ase (anaasε ebi rewu na ebi nso te ase, anaa yεrewu na yεrewo ebi nom nso). Na ԑmma sԑ yεbɛnyane yεn."
  23,38,"Ɔnyε hwee, na mmom ᴐyԑ onipa a ͻretwa nkontompo ato Nyankopͻn soͻ, na yεnnye no nni (da)”."
  23,39,"Ɔkaa sε. “Me Wura Nyankopͻn, boa me fa nkontompo a wͻbu me no ho.“"
  23,40,"Nyankopͻn kaa sε: “Ɛnkyε koraa wͻbɛnu wͻn ho “."
  23,41,"Enti nteamu no sͻͻ wͻn mu nokorε mu, na Yεyεε wͻn sε nwira (a yɛatwa ama no awoͻ). Enti nnipa bͻnefoͻ no frii hͻ."
  23,42,"Afei Yεbͻͻ awoͻ ntoatoasoͻ foforͻ wͻ wͻn akyi."
